ygData.messageBody:
Well,

I'm just assuming from the name that it woldnt be a guild i would like to
join, though i guess to be totally sure i would have to look at the
charter, but i thought it was said that the guild had nothing to do with
the name so that was my point but whatver, i've made too many enemies
here.

-joe
